
A *logical SQL server* is used by → Microsoft/Azure/products/SQL-Database and → Microsoft/Azure/products/Synapse-Analytics to administer the following properties in a set of databases:
  • logins
  • firewall rules
  • auditing rules
  • threat detection policies
  • auto-failover groups


links:
  → https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/logical-servers
